    detail: "This exceptional beachfront villa sits on one of Koh Samui's most tranquil stretches of coastline in Lipa Noi — 1.2 rai of prime beachfront land with 850 m² of refined indoor living designed for both privacy and grand entertaining. Contemporary architecture, expansive ocean views and direct beach access make it a standout among the island's west-coast homes, offered move-in ready and fully furnished.\n\nFive spacious en-suite bedrooms serve as private retreats, the master framing panoramic turquoise-sea views, while expansive living and dining areas flow outdoors through floor-to-ceiling windows so natural light and sea breezes define the interior. A fully equipped western kitchen with island counter complements the design for family living and high-end entertaining alike.\n\nAt its heart, a striking infinity pool merges visually with the sea beyond, with an outdoor terrace and jacuzzi for Samui's world-famous sunsets and direct access to Lipa Noi's soft sands. A dedicated laundry, separate staff quarters and generous storage round out the home, in a gated, managed, west-coast setting prized for calm, family-friendly beaches — with strong long-term value and rental appeal.",
