    detail: "A rare gem on one of Koh Samui's most beautiful and secluded white-sand beaches, this beachfront villa offers 28 metres of private frontage and uninterrupted sea views throughout the year. Set within an exclusive 24-hour gated residential estate with private access to an 800-metre stretch of pristine shoreline, the home combines unmatched privacy with exceptional convenience — just moments from Lamai town, yet hidden from tourist traffic. Only 200 metres down the beach, a stylish beach club offers dining, drinks and a peaceful social atmosphere, while a short stroll inland brings you to a premium sports and wellness club featuring a tennis court, gym, spa, restaurant and kids' club — with the rare benefit of room service delivered directly to your villa.\n\nWhite sand and lush tropical gardens surround this serene escape, designed for rest, rejuvenation and effortless island living. In a contemporary coastal style, the villa features glass doors and windows throughout, allowing the interior to merge beautifully with the surrounding greenery and ocean views. The open-plan living, dining and kitchen area is bright and spacious, decorated in crisp whites and soft blues for a clean, modern beach aesthetic, and the fully-equipped Western kitchen provides everything needed for cooking at home — or you can enjoy meal delivery and private chef services available within the estate.\n\nAll three bedrooms come with en-suite bathrooms: two feature king beds and direct terrace access, while the third includes twin beds — ideal for family or guests. The master offers garden and sea views, with sliding glass doors leading directly to the terrace. Outside, a generous sun terrace wraps around the villa with multiple zones for lounging and dining, and a traditional Thai-style beachside sala provides the perfect spot to enjoy the morning sunrise or unwind with an evening drink while listening to the waves.",
