    detail: "This is a rare opportunity to acquire a flat coastal plot on Koh Samui's increasingly sought-after west coast. Ideally positioned between Nathon and Lipa Noi, the land enjoys an impressive 59 metres of direct beachfront frontage — well suited to a private luxury residence or a low-density boutique development. Offered at ฿55,000,000, this Chanote-titled plot pairs strong development fundamentals with long-term investment appeal.\n\nWith a total land size of approximately 1-4-14.9 Rai (2,859.6 m²), the flat topography significantly reduces construction complexity and cost compared with the island's hillside sites, while the wide frontage allows unobstructed sea views, direct beach access and flexible architectural design. Local guidelines permit single-storey structures beyond a 10-metre coastal setback, individual footprints up to 75 m², and total coverage to 25% of the plot — ideal for an intimate villa compound or boutique resort that emphasises privacy, greenery and beachfront living.\n\nThe setting is quiet and established, in a neighbourhood of a limited number of high-end beachfront villas, minutes from Nathon town and the main ferry pier connecting Samui to the mainland. Cafés, restaurants, a Lotus's supermarket and a fresh market sit nearby, and the island's ring road is moments away. With beachfront supply on the west coast extremely limited, the plot stands out as a rare asset — for a lifestyle buyer, a developer, or long-term land banking.",
