    detail: "Set directly on the sand of Bophut Bay on Koh Samui's calm north coast, this is one of the island's largest private beachfront estates — four individually designed villas that can be booked together as a single gated compound for extended families, multi-generational celebrations and large groups of friends. Together they sleep up to forty guests across twenty en-suite bedrooms, with the flexibility to open or close wings to suit the party.\n\nThe estate's defining luxury is water: sixteen swimming and infinity pools thread between the villas and the beachfront, alongside expansive sun decks, shaded salas and lawns that run to the shoreline. Vast open-plan living and dining pavilions, multiple fully equipped kitchens and indoor-outdoor lounges give every group its own gathering space, while the absolute beachfront setting means warm, swimmable sea just beyond the deck.\n\nA full resident team looks after the stay end to end — estate manager, private chefs, housekeeping, security and a dedicated concierge for transfers, excursions, in-villa dining and events. Daily breakfast, high-speed WiFi and the run of the grounds are included, with Fisherman's Village dining and Bophut's restaurants a short drive away and the airport around twenty minutes from the gate.",
