    detail: "Villa 1 combines expansive living with panoramic views of Koh Samui's north-eastern coastline. Elevated above the shoreline, it offers seclusion and comfort while keeping Choeng Mon and Chaweng's beaches, dining and nightlife within easy reach. Its centrepiece is an L-shaped infinity pool — long enough for laps and perfectly positioned to frame the horizon — wrapped by expansive terraces, shaded outdoor pavilions and landscaped gardens that soften the villa's striking architecture.\n\nThree distinct lounge areas include a private cinema with projector and surround sound, a TV lounge and a quiet office space. The open-plan design lets guests gather in groups or retreat into smaller corners for downtime, while an outdoor sala, curved cocktail sofa and poolside BBQ set the scene for sociable evenings. Each of the five en-suite bedrooms is a private sanctuary with a king bed, oversized bathtub or rain shower and direct ocean views, sleeping up to 10 adults with options for children.\n\nKeeping active is easy with a private gym, a generous L-shaped lap pool and table tennis, while a Nuvo sound system runs throughout, alongside a full-service kitchen and bar. Private parking, full backup generators, uniformed security and complimentary WiFi round out a fully staffed, ultra-luxury hillside stay.",
