    detail: "This extraordinary seven-bedroom hillside retreat overlooks Koh Samui's north-eastern coastline with panoramic ocean views and one of the island's largest infinity pools. Designed for gatherings on a grand scale, it combines space, style and comfort in a setting that feels both secluded and connected — just minutes from the island's beaches, restaurants and nightlife.\n\nThe centrepiece is a 25-metre infinity-edge pool wrapped by expansive decks, a rooftop sun deck and landscaped gardens — endless opportunity for lazy afternoons in the sun and sunset dinners beneath the stars. Open-plan lounges and dining areas form a welcoming heart, while multiple pavilions and quiet corners let guests gather together or slip away for privacy. Each of the seven en-suite bedrooms is a private sanctuary, five with their own jacuzzis, all with terrace or balcony access; seven king beds sleep up to 14 adults.\n\nThe estate is built for sociable living and play: a commercial-grade gym with TRX, Hammer Strength and free weights, a private cinema, a games room with pool table, table tennis, arcade games and consoles, a poolside BBQ, a sunset cocktail deck, plus a yoga pavilion, massage sala and meditation nests. Private underground parking, full backup generators, uniformed security and complimentary WiFi complete a fully staffed, ultra-luxury hillside stay.",
