    detail: "Nestled in the enchanting Maenam district on Koh Samui's tranquil north coast, this modern five-bedroom villa is a tropical sanctuary blending luxury, comfort and awe-inspiring natural surroundings across an expansive 1,600 m² plot. Inside, five exquisitely furnished bedrooms each carry a private en-suite, with a dedicated kids' room of two bunk beds sleeping up to four children — comfortable for families and groups alike.\n\nThe villa's centrepiece is a striking 16-metre L-shaped infinity pool, thoughtfully positioned to maximise mesmerising views of the glistening sea and the island's celebrated sunsets. An open-air sala invites quiet moments amid the greenery, while a well-equipped gym, a foosball table, board games and a Devialet sound system keep every kind of guest entertained. High-speed WiFi covers the property, and each bedroom is finished with a safety box and refined details.\n\nA dedicated team of three including a private chef crafts culinary masterpieces to your taste, with daily housekeeping, a complimentary daily breakfast and turndown service. Minutes from Bang Po beach and a short drive from Fisherman's Village and Santiburi golf, it is an oasis of calm where panoramic sea views meet warm, attentive island hospitality.",
