    detail: "Situated along the pristine shores of Koh Samui, this beachfront estate is a seamless fusion of Balinese sophistication and tropical tranquility — top-of-the-line amenities paired with exclusive design and service. Its Balinese layout sets the stage for an immersive experience: a central courtyard graced by the azure sea and powdery white sand, wrapped in verdant foliage, inviting lounges and shaded enclaves, with a captivating pool of waterfall-style fountains at its heart.\n\nThe estate is divided into five beachfront suites — each with a private jacuzzi and direct beach access — and three suites with serene private gardens, eight en-suite bedrooms in all. A fully equipped gym and a wellness room with two massage tables, robes and oils keep guests active and pampered, while the sala and bar area, with a table for up to 18 and a six-seat bar, is made for gatherings. An outdoor kitchen with a high-end gas barbecue lets the private chef cook amid the natural beauty.\n\nA dedicated team of ten — personal manager, private chef, bartenders, housekeepers and security — attends to every need, with a 16-metre salt-treated pool, wine cellar, covered and beach lounges, and a movable big screen for meetings. Just 11 minutes from Samui Airport and minutes from Fisherman's Village, it is an idyllic seaside retreat where Balinese elegance meets tropical luxury.",
